Package ca.eshopexpress.model.dto

Class UserRegistrationDto

java.lang.Object
ca.eshopexpress.model.dto.UserRegistrationDto
public class UserRegistrationDto extends Object
Data Transfer Object (DTO) for handling user registration data. This class includes credentials, personal information, and related entities such as roles, orders, reviews, and wishlist items.
Since:
2025-05-09
